In the -Katta form, TAKAi is written TAKAkatta (the KA is lacking in your version).<br>
It may be strange sometimes to say so many KA.<br>
ATATAKAI (warm) will be ATATAKAKATTA. I don't know for you, but it's making me wondering if I'm actually saying something when I say that.<br>
